    answer: "Absolutely! We regularly help businesses finance multiple units simultaneously, whether it's a fleet of lorries, several excavators, or mixed equipment types. Bulk financing often comes with better terms. Many logistics companies finance 3-5 lorries at once, and construction firms finance multiple excavators through us."
