    answer: "Having existing loans doesn't automatically disqualify you. We evaluate your total debt service ratio, current income, and ability to service additional financing. Many of our clients have existing business loans, vehicle financing, or mortgages. What matters is manageable total debt relative to your income and cash flow."
  },

