  },
  {
    question: "Who owns the equipment during the financing period?",
    answer: "Under hire purchase financing, you own the equipment from day one and can use it for your business immediately. However, the financier holds a charge/lien on the equipment until full repayment. Once you complete all payments, the charge is removed, and you have full, unencumbered ownership with no further obligations."
